section_title: (1) ThisAct maybe called the Bharatiya Nyaya Sanhita, 2023.
content: 1. (1) ThisAct maybe called the Bharatiya Nyaya Sanhita, 2023. (2) It shall come intoforce on such date as the Central Government may, bynotification in the Official Gazette, appoint, and different dates maybe appointed for different provisions of this Sanhita.
